_sText:
[EN]The map has 64 spawn points,excellent fps,radar view.
I purposely made the map with just one bomb site because I had observed that on almost every defuse map the player prefer one bomb site over the other.
Special thanks to Wicked for testing my map on his server 86.105.192.115:27015
[RO]Harta are 64 de locuri,fps exelente,radar.
Dinadins am facut-o cu doar un singur loc de bomba deoarece am observat ca pe majoritatea hartilor jucatorii prefera mai mult un singur loc,celalalt sector de harta ramanand mai mult nefolosit.
Multumesc lui Wicked proprietarul si admin-ul serverului Astramania(86.105.192.115:27015) pt.favoarea de a imi testa harta.

ps

I will take a brake from mapping for a while,I don't know when I will start again.

enjoy!
